description: Demolition of buildings and redevelopment of land and buildings to provide a new building to comprise residential accommodation (Class C3 27,574sq.m comprising 284 units) and new educational and performance space for the Guildhall School of Music & Drama with ancillary plant and servicing and associated ancillary uses (Class D1 12,887sq.m); new retail floorspace (Class A1/A3 230sq.m); works of hard and soft landscaping, alterations to existing vehicular and pedestrian access and highway layout together with other associated and enabling works. (Amendments to scheme submitted December 2006).
